PrecisRESTRICTED WEAPON REGISTRATION CERTIFICATE FOR CLASSES OF PERSONS OTHER THAN INDIVIDUALS REGULATIONS prescribing a class of "persons other than individuals" who may be issued a Corporate Restricted Weapon Registration Certificate under section 109.1 of the Criminal Code which will allow prescribed corporations to acquire and possess restricted firearms in their own right as corporate entities.
